data.description: Home sweet home... nice and clean 2/2/2 with a split floor plan is situated on a corner lot in a neighborhood that's located conveniently near many amenities and THE BUS route.  The main living & dining area features plant shelves, a coat closet and sliders to the Lanai. In the kitchen you'll find pretty stone counter tops & back splashes, an eat-in dining nook with several windows for light/views, and a door to the covered screened lanai that overlooks the privacy fenced back yard featuring a nice sized open pavered patio. Inside, the master suite features a walk-in closet, linen closet, 2 sinks with a vanity counter and an oversized step in shower. The Guest bedroom also has a walk-in closet. The guest bathroom has a tub/shower combo and a linen closet. There's a small walk-through room just inside from garage that could be a work/project or inside storage space. The spacious 2 car garage features privacy screens, auto door opener, pull down ladder for attic access, laundry area, sprinkler system timer, and bonus custom hurricane shutters. Some of the windows are newer.. Roof new Oct. 2016. A/c new Sept. 2012. NO HOA in this community, former community HOA has been dissolved. The area has a lot of restaurants, shopping, banking, and medical. Hernando County boasts a non commercialized coast line with public parks, beaches, boat ramps, marina's, fishing piers... Enjoy sunsets, picnics, swimming, fishing, boating, kayaking, canoeing, paddle boarding... look up the local attraction Weeki Wachee, Rogers Park, Jenkins Creek, Linda Pedersen, and Pine Island beach at the Gulf of Mexico.
